<h1 class="">
Beat the bloat: Get rid of that spare tyre... in just seven days
</h1>
<div class="lead-text">
<p class=""><p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Our easy but effective seven-day diet plan will help you lose up to 4 pounds in a week, so you look and feel great</p>
</div>
<div class="styleGroup span-15-5" >
<!-- Can pick up the first element because is searching for author name -->
</div>
<div class="tmRow social-media clearfix"
>
<a class="addthis_button_tweet"	tw:url="http://www.mirror.co.uk/lifestyle/dieting/beat-the-bloat-get-rid-of-that-spare-tyre-892679"
tw:via="DailyMirror"
tw:text="Beat%20the%20bloat%3A%20Get%20rid%20of%20that%20spare%20tyre...%20in%20just%20seven%20days"
tw:related="3am"
tw:count="horizontal"	tw:counturl="http://www.mirror.co.uk/lifestyle/dieting/beat-the-bloat-get-rid-of-that-spare-tyre-892679">
</a>
<div class="fb-like" data-href="http://www.mirror.co.uk/lifestyle/dieting/beat-the-bloat-get-rid-of-that-spare-tyre-892679"
data-send="true"
data-layout="button_count" data-width="" data-action="like"
data-colorscheme="light"
data-show-faces="false" data-font="trebuchet ms">
</div>
